                  <font color="#00FF00">X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Hide Hole stats -
                  <font color="#00FF00">L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">VALKYRIE NO BOUKEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Shield -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump -
                  <font color="#00FF00">X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Shoot -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open chests / Talk / Run -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Crouch -
                  <font color="#00FF00">R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move character -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-Pad</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">PAC-ATTACK CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Rotate piece -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move piece left, right or down -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-Pad</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">KING OF KINGS CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Zoom In / Zoom Out -
                  <font color="#00FF00">L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Status -
                  <font color="#00FF00">R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select movement -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Unit status -
                  <font color="#00FF00">R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select place to move unit -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-pad</font><br><br>
&nbsp;</td>
